    "description": "In an attempt to escape from poverty Melinda infiltrated Salguro's Castle, now, she must escape it. <br><strong>Become an agile dual-wielder of magic artifacs</strong> and fight the many minions of <strong>The Sulgeri Witches</strong> as well as a parasitic force that prowls the halls of the castle...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168070/extras/57acb6ed34596ea6e0853d06002ad026.poster.avif?t=1721930554\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168070/extras/57acb6ed34596ea6e0853d06002ad026.webm?t=1721930554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168070/extras/57acb6ed34596ea6e0853d06002ad026.mp4?t=1721930554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><strong>Sorceress</strong> is an immersive first person action-adventure game focused on <strong>improvisation through creative use of elemental magic and flexible systems.</strong> Step into the boots of Melinda, and become a nimble quickwitted mage, cast spells from your arsenal of weapons and cause demise on your enemies while traversing the halls and corridors of Salguro's Castle, looking for a way to free Melinda from her disease...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168070/extras/367e9e22cb2806231a14032d83da409c.avif?t=1721930554\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore a wide assortment of <strong>hand-crafted</strong> levels, each with unique elements and optional challenges<br></li><li>Fight the resilient <strong>Parasite</strong> that has taken home on the castles' corridors and collect its precious spores</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168070/extras/1a3c8bb4c7f606e037cc39588628f50c.avif?t=1721930554\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Magic Weapons</strong> to manipulate physics and cause elemental reactions<br></li><li><strong>Customize</strong> your <strong>loadout</strong> and get creative to have an edge in combat<br></li><li><strong>Combine spells</strong> and be crafty to make the most out of your actions</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168070/extras/e3fad8ebc96586c9524449f72ccd5ba5.avif?t=1721930554\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Jump</strong>, <strong>run</strong>, <strong>kick</strong> and <strong>dash</strong>. Be agile and weave through the battlefield<br></li><li>Fire sources, electric machinery, crates and barrels, everything is <strong>interactable</strong>!<br></li><li>Steal your enemies' weapons and throw them back or keep them for later</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168070/extras/d876959b8f46318833886d0727939915.poster.avif?t=1721930554\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168070/extras/d876959b8f46318833886d0727939915.webm?t=1721930554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168070/extras/d876959b8f46318833886d0727939915.mp4?t=1721930554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
